{"tid":174725,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"前學民仔現身林鄭競選辦慶功宴","createTime":"2017-03-27T04:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:42:47.000Z","uid":5701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4da7f0f272aec20335b14e2ee4e042c653e2d589","tid":174725,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"【前學民仔現身林鄭競選辦慶功宴】<br />\n<br />\n放棄原則的那張嘴面，實在十分可怕。我常告戒自已，千萬不要成為自已曾經討厭的人。<br />\n<br />\n副本抄送：林鄭月娥競選辦公室Benson Luk及Marco Li<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n2012年TVB訪問李俊霖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshua1013/posts/10209848149373430\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshua1013%2Fposts%2F10209848149373430&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=17217e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshua1013/posts/10209848149373430</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《是日新聞：為奶媽站台學生 原來係黃絲？》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170326/56483501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170326%2F56483501&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=edd251fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170326%2F56483501&h=8d6fbc53\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170326/56483501</a><br />\n<br />\n在林鄭今天的慶功宴上，也有前「學民仔」的身影。與林鄭一起舉勝利手勢合照的李俊霖，今個學年一度參選教育大學學生會，在競選內閣擔任會長，今年一月卻以經常到外國為由退莊。有學民思潮前成員向《蘋果》確認，李曾在金鐘參與佔領運動。<br />\n李俊霖2012年以學民思潮義工身份接受《蘋果》訪問，斥梁振英玩弄語言偽術、任人唯親。他當時形容中學生已醒覺，「就好似沉睡嘅獅子，呢股力量開始抬頭，可以影響另一群人，左右政府政策」，呼籲市民參與2013年元旦遊行。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【為正策士集梁粉奶粉 包括前學民仔李俊霖】<br />\n2017年壹仔報導<br />\n<br />\n成員則包括前學民仔李俊霖（Marco），他亦被盛傳正為林鄭助選。據了解，李俊霖是當年被學民唯一一個革退的成員，「Marco係好想上位嘅人，成日都喺學民玩權鬥。一三年學民喺街頭公民抗命，前面啲人喺度瞓馬路，佢喺後面叫人走，因為佢自己唔想俾人拉。Benson就收留呢啲喺社運圈上唔到位嘅人。」一名前學民成員說。 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭今次參選來得非常倉促，主因是梁振英忽然被北京通知連任無望。據了解，當日林鄭說重新考慮出選之時，陸瀚民亦「收到order」要幫林鄭埋班，包括找來前僱主、世聯顧問行政總裁麥黃小珍加入團隊，「Benson之前喺世聯做過，林鄭做發展局局長時，有幾個project就係同世聯合作，包括市區重建策略檢討，佢同林鄭一早已經識。」事實上，麥黃小珍是林鄭的大學同窗，外界一直指她是林鄭的公關大臣，但其實她也是被牽線而加入團隊，而陸就一直扮演中間人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/2_482921_0?EDM=EDITORIAL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fce2017.appledaily.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2_482921_0%3FEDM%3DEDITORIAL&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2282d475\" target=\"_blank\">http://ce2017.appledaily.com.hk/articles/2_482921_0?EDM=EDITORIAL</a><br />\n<br />\n【90後新世代李俊霖：不倒梁國教必重來】<br />\n2012年蘋果訪問<br />\n<br />\n中六生李俊霖是學民思潮義工，佔領政總期間，他當司儀，帶領市民喊口號，也曾站在台上向母親道歉。李俊霖說，當師奶也對梁振英反感時，可見這政府有多不濟。近月中央政策組下令所有政府公職任命，都要知會全職顧問高靜芝，他們這班中學生也看穿梁用人唯親，「委任所有『梁粉』入局，所有政策都偏向梁振英一個人」。當這種政治審批伸延至校長、校監，全屬梁的「自己人」，「結果好簡單，學生嘅意見反映唔到，國民教育會捲土重來」。<br />\n<br />\n反國教運動後，李俊霖發現身邊多了同學對社會議題表達意見，包括新界東北發展及守護龍尾等；他以前會覺得社會上總有其他人代替自己發聲，但經過反國教一役，醒覺中學生的力量可以很大，再不是乳臭未乾被忽略的一群，「就好似沉睡嘅獅子，呢股力量開始抬頭，可以影響另一群人，左右政府政策」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121228/18116268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121228%2F18116268&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=bfbc6c88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121228%2F18116268&h=83219c13\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121228/18116268</a><br />\n<br />\n相片來源：蘋果日報【獨家慶功宴】林鄭開香檳慶祝 奶粉爭住攬 <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170326/56483087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170326%2F56483087&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=cfede68f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170326%2F56483087&h=7ede15e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170326/56483087</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/123520_8bc323619b8b7bf0e764b5344c5fa972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F123520_8bc323619b8b7bf0e764b5344c5fa972.jpg&h=b0023d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCredit: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshua1013/posts/10209847552358505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshua1013%2Fposts%2F10209847552358505&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2c2eff72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshua1013/posts/10209847552358505</a>"},{"pid":"56cc83128029feb9c708b41bb1e2b615a6bb7282","tid":174725,"uid":5701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80cad729a8a692a8409d48cae80ab00a71aed63c","tid":174725,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"證明佢真係招攬唔同政治立場既賢才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f247ddbfb7f30d599c3a41df7592d3dfabb5fc","tid":174725,"uid":78712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39pO327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39pO327.jpg&h=6f14d5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b707b29df0300c45393e1b447d3ddc457a922fc0","tid":174725,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39pO327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39pO327.jpg&h=6f14d5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr